In certain rare instances, such as if you received a defective product, we may request that you return a product for examination, in which case we will provide a shipping label. Alternatively, we may ask that you provide photos of the product labels, including lot number and expiration date, and a detailed description of any damage reported

Members of the Chopra Club are entitled to a 10% discount on all items they purchase through a Program Consultant or at chopra.com, subject to a $250 maximum discount per order (or event in the case of a retreat), with the limited exceptions of Chopra App subscriptions and the Chopra Health Retreat. In the event a Chopra Club member is a Chopra Certified (Meditation or Health) Teacher or Chopra Certified Health and Wellness Coach, the discount will apply to the net purchase price after factoring in the applicable Teacher or Coach discount. Chopra Club members may also receive additional offers and access to certain Materials in our sole discretion subject to any particular offers and terms as may be provided at the point of sale or any purchase confirmation. You should see your discount reflected on your pre-purchase confirmation or otherwise have your discount communicated to you prior to completing your purchases. Please contact us at for any issues. Once your order is complete, you will not be able to retroactively receive your Chopra Club discount.
